title: Allocate 1,000 JAMM per week for newsletter contributions
body:
I propose that we allocate 1,000 JAMM per week for newsletter contributions. This will be allocated to members who provide insights to a newsletter issue in the rough-drafts channel on the JAMM Discord. It will be distributed via SourceCred.

This proposal can be amended through a community vote with equal or higher quorum.
author: 0x10D6d2e343281D388291A3e02f3293AaEdA67178
